{"tid":765624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"錦户亮偷睡人妻兩年 露點床照流出","createTime":"2018-08-03T02:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T07:28:18.000Z","uid":69256,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7b36307deeed64a52d74f41507e6871f31a33b90","tid":765624,"uid":69256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n傑尼斯男團「關8」歷經主唱澀谷昴退團、成員安田章大開腦手術與骨折傷癒，將於9月來台獻出海外首唱，此時又爆出不倫醜聞。33歲錦戶亮被爆和有孩子的人妻偷情2年，露點床照曝光。<br />\n<br />\n據《FRIDAY》報導，錦戶亮每個月都會回關西和20多歲的人妻M子幽會。M子的閨蜜爆料稱，M子承受不了罪惡感，找閨蜜商量，還秀出錦戶亮的裸身床照當證據。<br />\n<br />\n爆料內容指出，錦戶亮6年前於大阪的俱樂部搭訕在廣告代理商工作的M子，「當時他渾身充滿『幹勁』，M子因隔天要早起上班，與他搭小黃抵達旅館下車後立刻說再見落跑」。<br />\n<br />\n相隔4年錦戶亮與M子在酒吧偶然重逢，女方禁不住他猛烈示愛，在他下榻飯店第一次發生肉體關係，之後兩人幾乎每個月密會一次，直到今年M子才對閨蜜吐露搞不倫的罪惡感，閨蜜勸她應該與錦戶亮切斷關係，但某天M子哭說「真的愛上他了」，又捨不得小孩，一直處於掙扎中。<br />\n<br />\n閨蜜擔心M子再與錦戶亮糾纏下去絕對會不幸，也認為錦戶亮完全不過問M子的老公、小孩，根本只是把她當砲友，無法原諒身為人氣偶像的他害了一個女人的人生，才會出面爆料，藉此強迫M子與他分手。<br />\n<br />\n不過因錦戶亮玩咖形象深植人心，被爆睡人妻，日本網友大多不意外，有人認為女方閨蜜當抓耙仔「毋通」，甚至有人檢討女主角，有小孩還去俱樂部飲酒作樂；只能說「人帥真好」。（娛樂中心／綜合報導）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180803/1403764/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180803%2F1403764%2F&d=EcPZaEoD0XJ%2BoQ%2BnfGpsrZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e3c03b85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180803%2F1403764%2F&h=bfc22b7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180803/1403764/</a>"},{"pid":"4e3b5526d361a8b3ef1c134a9ede3ddc6847bad4","tid":765624,"uid":11381,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"那個了唷"},{"pid":"43f0706416bd60741baa79455162219b1070ad70","tid":765624,"uid":69256,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/105252_209aa3a9ebb7cd40dc21fd8dc2bb6636.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F105252_209aa3a9ebb7cd40dc21fd8dc2bb6636.png&h=7226832d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b25d6b33d623bc760cb37473317378c345a6f93b","tid":765624,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188c01aef6995f00ba07131a0b042114ee29e2a2","tid":765624,"uid":21247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430a8136a38454fe041a1c3e1ddf7f92ea4d12f8","tid":765624,"uid":60982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"也認為錦戶亮完全不過問M子的老公、小孩，根本只是把她當砲友，無法原諒身為人氣偶像的他害了一個女人的人生，才會出面爆料，藉此強迫M子與他分手。<br />\n<br />\n女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2419cff203fe6fc2e6cdadf2577d380319669f27","tid":765624,"uid":120918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"男人lin圖就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb291861ed3b2ff6d27d0939e3f88887cecda9c","tid":765624,"uid":115910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:51:03.000Z","msg":"真係有圖,但與我所想的不一樣呢"},{"pid":"61797266889a6c2dd7400bf9e9a0f579df9ea63b","tid":765624,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:51:30.000Z","msg":"賤女人"},{"pid":"75430cb92fe4c21112962a206d9c4eddaf9b62f9","tid":765624,"uid":39576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"結衣揀達哥真係好明智"},{"pid":"1de2d4d0a775acdc40a8c0bedd08d674c8b27293","tid":765624,"uid":112551,"like":0,"di